The fact that the technical director of the Eastern and deputy general director of the CENKI for technological development Andrey Ohlopkov moved to work in the Hrunitschev State Nuclear Power Center, "Kommersant" told top managers of several enterprises of the space industry, as well as an employee of the government apparatus.
"He's been working in his new position for several weeks", said industry sources.
We were unable to obtain an operational comment from the CENIC on Thursday, and Mr. Ohlopkov himself was unavailable for comment.
